Given a string where words are separated by any of the _, -, characters.
Write a function that converts such string to single studly caps case word. For example
Input:
The quick-brown_fox jumps over the_lazy-dog
Output:
TheQuickBrownFoxJumpsOverTheLazyDog
Your solution:
should contain PHP function with solution. Use type hinting and return type declaration with strict mode enabled.